snippet.title: DUO v2 (Windows game 2007)
snippet.description:
DUO is a shooting game by Binary Zoo Studios.
The object is to eliminate all the balls (enemies) in each level.
After each ball dies, it offers two items such as weapon powerup, health powerup.
It has 25 different weapons. (purple, red, green, blue, white)

The player can rotate the shooting direction.
